      "n": 12,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad patiks tam Kehni-\nam taws Skaistums/ jo wiꞥſch\nrr taws KUNGS/ untew buhs\nwiꞥſchu peeluhtag.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta Meita no Zora buhs\nlaht ar Dahwanahm/ tee Bag-\ngatee ſtarp Laudim tawa Preek-\ncha peeluhtag.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſs Skaistums ta Keh-\nitra Meitas irr Eekſchpuſſê/\nwiꞥſas Apgehrbs irr no rakſtita\nSelta Darba.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta tohp eeſch iſraksti-\nahm Drehbehm pee ta Kehnina\nvaddita/ wiꞥſas Drangainas\nabs Jumprawas/ kas wiꞥſai\nakkat eet/ tohp pee tewi westas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tahs taps ar Preeku un\nihgſmibu wadditas/ un ee-ees\nekſch ta Kehnira skaista Raiña.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tawu Tehwu Weetá\nuhs tew Dehli/ tohs eezelfi tu\nar Leeleem-Kungeem pahr wiſu\nSemni.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Es peeninneschii tawu\nBahrdii lihds wiﬀeem Behruu\nBehrneem/ tadeht pateiks tew\nce Laudis muhſchigi muhſchani.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": �,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ta XLVI. Dseefma.\nJeena Pateikſchanas, un Eepreezinachanas,\nDseefma/ eeſch ka ta Deewa Draudse Dee.\ntawm pateiz/ ka tas to lihdſſchim no teem Ee,\nnaidneekem paſargajs/ un issakka/ ka ta fa\nwu Zerribu ween us Deewu leek : 2.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": �,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "W Eena Dseefma preeſch\nW ta augsta Dseedataja/\nstarp teem Behrneem\norus/ us Alamohi.\n2. Deews irr muhfu Patwe-\nums un Stiprums/ ihsti klaht\n"
    },
    {
      "n": �,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "buhdains warrens Paligs Beh-\ndu Laika.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tadeht mehs ne bihsta-\nmees/jepſchu arri ta Semne pa-\njustu/ un tee Kalni paſchá Juu-\nras Widdú nogrintu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Jepſchu wiꞥſas Uhdeng\nkahtu/ un ſajauks taptu/ un\nno wiꞥſas Gresnoschanas tee\nKalni drebbetu/ Sela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tatschu tahs Uppes\nStrautini to Deewa Pilſſahtu\neepreezinahs/ kur ta wiſu-aug-\nſtaka ſwehtas Weetas Dsihwo-\nkſi irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Deetws irr wiꞥſa Widdú/\nwiꞥſch ne fchaubifees / Deetws\nwiꞥſam palihdſehs agri.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Teem Pagaxeem jakanz/\nun tahm Walſtibahm jatakiht /\ntaiSemmet ja-iſkuhſt/kad wiꞥſch\ntawu Balsfi iſlaisch.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS Zebaäts\nirr ar mums/ tas Deetws Jehka-\nba irr muhſu augſtajs Patwe-\nrums/ Sela.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Nahzeet / un raugajt ta\nKUNGA Darbus/ kas Pohsti-\nſchanu wirs Semmes fuhta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kas Kaṙrus leek mittetees\nzaur wiﬀu Paſauli/ kas Stoḫ-\npus falauſch/ un Schkehpus fa-\ndausa/ kas Rattus ar Ugguni\ntadedſina.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Mittejeetees un afsibſteet\nka es Deetws efmu / es buhſchu\npa-augſtinahts ſtarp teem Paga-\nxeem/ es buhſchu pa-augſtinahts\nSemmes Wirſu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tas KUNGS Zebaäts Re\nSſſſſſ 3 irr\n"
    }
  ],
